title: The Secret She Can't Hide by India Grey
description:
World-famous racing driver Cristiano Maresca "always" spent the night before a race in the arms of a beautiful woman...One night three years ago that woman was Kate Edwards, and her time with Cristiano awakened her to unimaginable pleasure. But the following day the untamable Cristiano had a near-fatal crash...and then Kate discovered she was expecting his baby....

Now Monte Carlo is set to celebrate Cristiano's return to the track. Shivering with nerves, Kate braves the paparazzi to find the man who set her body aflame--and tell him her scandalous secret....
Italy's most notorious playboy has a love child.

Genre: Romance
